{"tid":1286551,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"切勿騎劫77遊行","createTime":"2019-07-05T01:49:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-05T17:46:39.000Z","uid":209318,"like":94,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"93654b2b4e5d2fd162781890fda9931f7bed0dbb","tid":1286551,"uid":209318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T01:49:43.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">集中五大訴求</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">身而為人,關心其他受難既人係理所當然<br />\n但此時此刻為香港及香港人發聲先係最為重要<br />\n大家可以幫手係網上轉發,可以同親朋好友講<br />\n但唔好係香港咁重要既時刻大愛病發,騎劫遊行<br />\n你忘記左先行離去既戰友?<br />\n你忘記左被捕既戰友?<br />\n你忘記左五大訴求無一回應?<br />\n你忘記左香港為何落得如此下場?</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">77遊行 集中五大訴求</span><br />\n勿忽然大愛 勿讓大家既努力白白浪費<br />\n大家請諗下,焦點轉移最大得益者係邊個?"},{"pid":"49433951ed5a5dbd434347b84187ac271062746a","tid":1286551,"uid":200758,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T01:50:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OJfWtfJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOJfWtfJ.jpg&h=3b2d02f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r6QrQt4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr6QrQt4.jpg&h=02ad2ebb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5ofWuem.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5ofWuem.png&h=f545a766&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a6e441d55bd6dc4e39c7901d6839bd63905def1d","tid":1286551,"uid":209318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T01:51:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"43d5db4b83ae7101081406ec806f7d4e11f823ad","tid":1286551,"uid":147248,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T01:53:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>如果班撚屌大中華膠三毛7.7當日攪武漢<br />\n我唔會唔黎，因為會中計，會浪費左申請不反對通知書巴打既心血<br />\n但我一定會逐個屌柒佢地屌撚到你收皮為止</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n明明之前每次出黎都大大聲<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>HONG KONG IS NOT CHINA</strong></span></span><br />\n而家無啦啦聲援鄰國個垃圾場<br />\n大中華膠三毛收皮！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔好俾人騎劫我地儲左咁耐既政治能量！</span><br />\n<br />\n－ － － － －<br />\n五大訴求<br />\n一、徹底撤回修例<br />\n二、收回暴動定義<br />\n三、撤銷對今為所有反送中抗爭者控罪<br />\n四、徹底追究警隊濫權情況<br />\n五、以行政命令解散立法會，立即實行雙真普選"},{"pid":"72766c990aff03ee1680dff59948d09cb3d5222c","tid":1286551,"uid":148987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T01:54:19.000Z","msg":"武漢人：港獨分子唔好諗住利用我地<br />\n<br />\n大家唔好自作多情<br />\n<br />\n要撐就撐分離主義滬獨川獨疆獨圖獨台獨<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n集中五大訴求<br />\n一、徹底撤回修例<br />\n<br />\n二、收回暴動定義<br />\n<br />\n三、撤銷對今為所有反送中抗爭者控罪<br />\n<br />\n四、徹底追究警隊濫權情況<br />\n<br />\n五、以行政命令解散立法會，立即實行雙真普選<br />\n0<br />\n0"},{"pid":"ca0bde0dd9885fcb46dbe3855dcc84c2d0499c6a","tid":1286551,"uid":209318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T02:03:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3b63a36bafaebe473e12d589cf1ac1b7cacb2dd4","tid":1286551,"uid":209318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T02:12:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5a1366a2d67fbe97a0c6d56104a4b4f3d21adfd2","tid":1286551,"uid":54181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T02:12:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6396af341f077631ffe2b530c3851432d4b95883","tid":1286551,"uid":147248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T02:13:17.000Z","msg":"好多人話7.7聲援武漢就唔去，唔好中計！更加要去！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1286615\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1286615</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"bfc0a3c487a0be257b5f2819e15ac2b58a10e29e","tid":1286551,"uid":209318,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T02:13:18.000Z","msg":"次次出黎都叫HK IS NOT CHINA<br />\n而家無啦啦支援武漢?<br />\n你地精神分裂定3毛入侵呀?<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">集中五大訴求</span>"},{"pid":"4e30205ea3dd1d87db419cc0db54d8fb786ad415","tid":1286551,"uid":70888,"like":0,"